name: Kirstin's Projects
body: ### Welcome to the my repository! This page serves as a portal to various project pages. If you need access to a project contact [me](kirstin.holsman@noaa.gov). *** ### Getting Started with GitHub 1. Create an account and login at https://github.com. 2. Download git or github desktop at https://desktop.github.com to manage versions or simply download the repository 3. To access my repositories email me for access HERE. *** ### [ACLIM:The Alaska CLIMate Change Project](https://kholsman.github.com/ACLIM_site/ACLIM.html) This project represents a comprehensive, collaborative effort to characterize climate-change effects on the Bering Sea ecosystem, from physics to fisheries, and to understand how different fisheries management approaches might attenuate or amplify climate driven changes to fish and shellfish biomass. ***
